==English==

===Noun Phrase===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[endosymbiotic]] [[theory]]'''

#''Ecology.'' The theory that concerns the origins of [[mitochondrion|mitochondria]] and [[chloroplast]]s, which are [[organelle]]s of [[eukaryotic]] cells.

